Uses of Package
inputmdxml.temporary

  • Packages that use inputmdxml.temporary 
    Package Description
    inputmdxml
    Contains the main converter class which calls the actual converter classes
    inputmdxml.converter.element
    Contains converter classes converting PackagedElements and their child elements to UmlElements
    inputmdxml.converter.relationship
    Contains converter classes converting PackagedElements and their child elements to UmlRelationships
  • Classes in inputmdxml.temporary used by inputmdxml 
    Class Description
    TemporaryModel
    Auxiliary class managing references of UmlElements, UmlTemplateParameters, UmlRelationships, UmlAttributes and UmlParameters
    These references are used for the replacement with the actual elements
  • Classes in inputmdxml.temporary used by inputmdxml.converter.element 
    Class Description
    TemporaryModel
    Auxiliary class managing references of UmlElements, UmlTemplateParameters, UmlRelationships, UmlAttributes and UmlParameters
    These references are used for the replacement with the actual elements
    TemporaryTemplateBinding
    Extends the UmlTemplateBinding with a map containing references to the UmlTemplateParameter and type of the UmlTemplateBindings parameter substitution
  • Classes in inputmdxml.temporary used by inputmdxml.converter.relationship 
    Class Description
    TemporaryModel
    Auxiliary class managing references of UmlElements, UmlTemplateParameters, UmlRelationships, UmlAttributes and UmlParameters
    These references are used for the replacement with the actual elements
    TemporaryRelationship
    Auxiliary class extending the UmlRelationship with references to the client element and supplier element since the resolving of all references is only possible after all UmlElements have been converted
